      "instruction": "<p>While everything's cooking, chop your <strong>coriander </strong>finely, including the stalks</p><p>Cut your<strong> green chilli[es]</strong> in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop finely</p>",
