    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and roughly shred</p><p>Chop your <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Top, tail, and grate your <strong>carrot[s]</strong></p><p>Trim, then finely slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong></p>",
